Analysis For IMDB Dataset¶

  • In this project ,I wil analyze dataset containing performance metrics for individual posts.

TMDB Dataset Field Description¶

  • Below is a description of the column fields in the dataset

core fields¶

  • Impressions: Number of times the post was seen.
  • Reach: Number of unique accounts that saw the post.
  • Profile Visits: Number of users who visited the profile .
  • Follows: Number of new followers gained from the post.
  • Likes, Comments, Shares, Saves: Types of engagement.
  • Caption: Text content of the post.
  • From Home, From Hashtags, From Explore, From Other Sources: Breakdown of reach sources.
  • Date: Date the post was published.

Quiestion to be answered¶

1- Which posts have the highest engagement rate?

2- What are the top sources of reach?

3- did there a relationship between engagement and follows?

4- Which caption themes perform best?

5- What time periods show the highest engagement?

6- Which posts drive the most profile visits?

7- What are the characteristics of high-performing posts?

8- How does reach diversity affect performance?

9- Which types of engagement (likes, comments, saves) are most common?

10- Can we predict follows based on impressions and engagement?

df["Engagement"] = df["Likes"] + df["Comments"] + df["Shares"] + df["Saves"]
df["Engagement Rate"] = df["Engagement"] / df["Impressions"]
df["Reach Diversity"] = df[["From Home", "From Hashtags", "From Explore"]].std(axis=1)

def categorize(caption):
    caption = caption.lower()
    if "python" in caption or "code" in caption:
        return "Programming"
    elif "finance" in caption or "money" in caption:
        return "Finance"
    elif "career" in caption or "job" in caption:
        return "Career"
    else:
        return "Other"

df["Category"] = df["Caption"].apply(categorize)

Insights from this data :-¶

1- Engagement drivers (posts with high likes and shares and clear pictures and short contant )

2- saves and shre are strong indicators for contant value

3- Content Timing ( posts are published in weekends or eveining show hier engagement and profile vists more than ather time )

Some Recommendations :-¶

1- Hashtag and Explore ( targetd hashtags to increase reach from followers )

2- Content Strategy ( focus on posts that include save and shares these are high engement signals)

3- Profile Funnel ( post durindg peak engagement hours based on your best time )

4- Reach Source Breakdown( Majority of reach comes From Home meaning followers are seeing your content )
